  "description": "makes the use of rockets better",
  "body": "# Rocket Utlis\n<p>\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\">\n<img alt=\"fabric-api\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/yacl\">\n<img alt=\"fabric-api\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Danrus1100/durability_visibility_options/refs/heads/dev/assets/YACL.svg\">\n</a>\n</center>\n</p>\n<p><center><a href=\"https://discord.gg/sBpHZUBebQ\"><img alt=\"discord-singular\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\">\n</a></center></p>\n\n\n**This mod turns off unnecessary (in my opinion) interaction with rockets:**\n\n1. Sneak-only interaction\n![demo1](https://github.com/Danrus1100/RocketUtils/raw/main/assets/demo1.gif)\n2. Using through grass and other non-colide blocks\n![demo2](https://github.com/Danrus1100/RocketUtils/raw/main/assets/demo2.gif)\n\n# Lithium compatibility\n\nSome things don't work by default if you use Lithium. To fix this, open the `.minecraft/config/lithium.properties` file and add to it:\n\n```properties\nmixin.world.raycast=false\n```\n\n## Try my other mods: \n<a href=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d6a47959d6cd10725f3d7545da68276e23e6fc00.png\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a6dae3716505b7221af13b6f5f4aae1bcb71e028.png\" alt=\"destroy-item-white-list\" width=\"287px\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/durability_visibility_options\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8cae1332efddc92a0b627301f69521af24d1f934.png\" alt=\"durability_visibility_options\" width=\"319px\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rocket-utils\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4c7829b3b82784717731ef0ef50d9c5ec89471cf.png\" alt=\"rocket-utils\" width=\"223px\"/>\n</a>\n",
